I use ffmpegthumbnailer
`thumbgen () {
    ffmpegthumbnailer -i "$1" -o "${1%.*}.jpg" -q 5 -s 512 -t $2%
}`

or imagemagick for resizing
`convert $1 -resize $x% $2`

@Human Bean: Eh, we'll be fine. Not like the other years haven't been a piece of shit.
As for death rate, it's high every year. Usually murder and dengue outbreaks.
Thanks for the good wishes, though. It'll help.
